{"tid":2428883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：趙婷奪金球獎最佳導演創下歷史　各地亞裔網民祝賀","createTime":"2021-03-02T01:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T02:15:04.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"081b082a79cd883f51aeea2415d44969cf12c446","tid":2428883,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n華人導演趙婷憑劇情片浪跡天地，奪得金球獎最佳導演，創下金球獎歷史。<br />\n<br />\n浪跡天地講述一名女子因經濟不景失去所有，以居住在貨車的現代遊牧民身分，遊歷美國西部。<br />\n<br />\n現年38歲的趙婷生於北京，現時在美國居住。她是歷來第二名奪得金球獎最佳導演的女性，並且是首位贏得金球獎最佳導演的亞洲女性。浪跡天地是她的第3部劇情作品，她近期執導漫威電影永恆族。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>全球各地的亞裔網民祝賀趙婷，有人說趙婷的成就為亞裔年輕女子帶來極大鼓舞，有人就說期待她下一部得獎作品。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578124-20210301.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578124-20210301.htm&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=0d6b781e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578124-20210301.htm&h=f5f7cdbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578124-20210301.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ba1794f71615de6ce2e267ec7f583c68f017ac00","tid":2428883,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:38:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">等睇好快：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各地猿猴類祝賀.......</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5a6c1ca627baa74dcb278f0cce9eddba86be5dd6","tid":2428883,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:49:47.000Z","msg":"各地支那人慶祝咋話？"},{"pid":"7418612c1fc6f39ccc638981df5cfacb323cbdf2","tid":2428883,"uid":33222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"佢中